spirit creatures. When displeased, jinushigami can eradicate
trails and warp the contours of their terrain, forcing
travelers to endure unreasonable hardship in travel. These
goliaths have little patience for those who would defile their
efforts, and offenders who fail to listen to a jinushigami's
initial hints quickly discover how devastating the kami's
