The hideous penanggalen is one of the most horrific
vampiric monstrosities. By day, a penanggalen appears
to be a normal humanoid, but at night or when provoked,
the creature's head rips free from the rest of her body,
coils of viscera and entrails dangling from her throat
as she launches into the air, seeking blood to sate her
unholy thirst.
Unlike most undead, the penanggalen is more akin to
the lich in that she willfully abandons both her mortality
and morality to become a hideous undead monster.
